OL,3,CPlans press on to reopen Oxford
OL,4,Cimmigration removal centre
OL,6,FCampaigners protesting at a public
OL,7,Fevent say the reopening of an
OL,8,Fimmigration removal centre near Oxford
OL,9,Fis 'destined to fail' and the site
OL,10,Fshould be put to better use.
OL,12,FCampsfield House in Kidlington closed
OL,13,Fdown seven years ago, after complaints
OL,14,Fabout conditions, riots and escapes.
OL,16,FHowever, the Home Office is pressing
OL,17,Fahead with plans to reopen and expand
OL,18,Fit.
