OL,3,CPlans press on to reopen Oxford
OL,4,Cimmigration removal centre
OL,6,FA public engagement event has been
OL,7,Ftaking place this afternoon where
OL,8,Flocal residents can see the proposals
OL,9,Fand meet the project team.
OL,11,FThere have been fierce arguments for
OL,12,F32 years about whether or not there
OL,13,Fshould be an immigration detention
OL,14,Fcentre or removal centre at Campsfield
OL,15,FHouse and today's engagement event has
OL,16,Fbrought the issues into focus once
OL,17,Fmore.
