OL,3,CPlans press on to reopen Oxford
OL,4,Cimmigration removal centre
OL,6,FThe Home Office information session
OL,7,Fhere today explains Campsfield House
OL,8,Fwill mostly house men described as
OL,9,F"offenders", two to a room held under
OL,10,Fimmigration powers who will not be
OL,11,Ffree to leave the site or go into the
OL,12,Flocal area, so it's a different
OL,13,Fsituation to asylum seeker hotels.
OL,15,FThe original site stopped being used
OL,16,Fback in 2018 after a number of serious
OL,17,Fincidents in its history and a mass
OL,18,Fescape as well and concerns about the
OL,19,Fwelfare of detainees.
