OL,3,CPlans press on to reopen Oxford
OL,4,Cimmigration removal centre
OL,6,FProtesters were back last year wanting
OL,7,Fit to stay closed, but today work is
OL,8,Fwell underway to refurbish the secure
OL,9,Fsite due to be opened in two phases,
OL,10,F160 beds in the refurbished building
OL,11,Fthen up to a further 400 in new build
OL,12,Fall said to meet environmental and
OL,13,Fsustainability targets.
OL,15,FNow, local councils, politicians and
OL,16,Ftrades unions have largely come out
OL,17,Fagainst reopening the site, but
OL,18,Fresidents in Kidlington have mixed
OL,19,Fviews.
