OL,3,CPlans press on to reopen Oxford
OL,4,Cimmigration removal centre
OL,6,FThe local Liberal Democrat MP, Calum
OL,7,FMiller, is also against reopening the
OL,8,Fsite. He said: "Local residents are
OL,9,Flooking forward to the opportunity to
OL,10,Fscrutinise what the Home Office are
OL,11,Fproposing.
OL,13,F"They're really angry that we have
OL,14,Fphase one going on at the moment -
OL,15,Fit's already been redeveloped and yet
OL,16,Fthe Home Office has not consulted and
OL,17,Fspoken with them.
