OL,3,CPlans press on to reopen Oxford
OL,4,Cimmigration removal centre
OL,6,F"I think it's incredibly important
OL,7,Fthat there is some degree of
OL,8,Fconsultation, and consent from local
OL,9,Fresidents, simply to explain why it's
OL,10,Fnecessary and how any project of this
OL,11,Fscale will be managed."
OL,13,FThe Home Office haven't published
OL,14,Fcosts, but protestors claim they
OL,15,Fcalculate Phase 1 alone to be #70
OL,16,Fmillion.
