OL,3,CPlans press on to reopen Oxford
OL,4,Cimmigration removal centre
OL,6,FA Home Office spokesperson said: "We
OL,7,Fare increasing detention and returns
OL,8,Fcapacity, including a 1,000 bed
OL,9,Fexpansion at Campsfield and Haslar,
OL,10,Fwith the first tranche of additional
OL,11,Fbeds coming online within months, to
OL,12,Fsupport many thousands more enforced
OL,13,Fremovals each year.
OL,15,F"Campsfield IRC will have a total
OL,16,Fcapacity of 400 beds.
OL,18,F"Around 160 bed spaces will be created
OL,19,Fin the refurbished accommodation with
OL,20,Ffurther expansion in future, for up to
OL,21,F400 beds in total.
